value.0: A well dressed man suited for expedition! Or, that's at least what one might think.  The emaculate state of his attire given the tropical climate in which he resides leads one to the conclusion he doesn't know the true meaning of hard work.  The second hint to this would be his floral scent.

Value.value: Pardon me, but I'm a bit busy tending to my supplies at the moment!

value.0: With vibrantly colored feathers, this bird is quick to catch a wandering eye.  One can only imagine that predators must have a field day spotting them.  Perhaps it's fortuitous that they can fly.
